# 配置说明 
## supervisor 配置
/etc/supervisor/conf.d/awesome.conf
```
[program:awesome] 	#指定服务名
#指定启动gunicorn的命令行，设定gunicorn的启动端口为9000，WSGI处理函数入口为wsgiapp:application
command     = /usr/bin/gunicorn --bind 127.0.0.1:9000 --workers 1 --worker-class gevent wsgiapp:application
directory   = /srv/awesome/www	#指定服务所在目录
user        = www-data	#
startsecs   = 3

redirect_stderr         = true
stdout_logfile_maxbytes = 50MB
stdout_logfile_backups  = 10
stdout_logfile          = /srv/awesome/log/app.log

```


## nginx 配置
* /etc/nginx/sites-available/awesome
```
server {
    listen      80; # 监听80端口

    root       /srv/awesome/www;
    access_log /srv/awesome/log/access.log;
    error_log  /srv/awesome/log/error.log;

    # server_name awesome.sysu.edu.cn; # 配置域名

    # 处理静态文件/favicon.ico:
    location /favicon.ico {
        root /srv/awesome/www;
    }

    # 处理静态资源:
    location ~ ^\/static\/.*$ {
        root /srv/awesome/www;
    }

    # 动态请求转发到9000端口(gunicorn):
    location / {
        proxy_pass       http://127.0.0.1:9000;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
    }
}
```

# 日志
* Nginx和App本身的log： /srv/awesome/log
* Supervisor日志： /var/log/supervisor


# 问题 
## mysql 无法启动
`service mysql start` 命令无法启动mysql
start: Rejected send message, 1 matched rules; type="method_call", sender=":1.81" (uid=1000 pid=3135 comm="start mysql ") interface="com.ubuntu.Upstart0_6.Job" member="Start" error name="(unset)" requested_reply="0" destination="com.ubuntu.Upstart" (uid=0 pid=1 comm="/sbin/init ")
解决方法：$ sudo start mysql 
